{"tid":1568724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"915 流動式超巨大連儂牆 ，we need you ！！！","createTime":"2019-09-14T11:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T16:38:30.000Z","uid":49898,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"ee2425a559925cb1ee83dd8c4e92ea094858a942","tid":1568724,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:10:05.000Z","msg":"雖然而家已經進入全面戰爭狀態<br />\n聽日遊行集會都俾狗反對左<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但我相信聽日會好多人出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n講少少今日嘅愛狗行動<br />\n好多人睇到今日出事都話要直接打反擊<br />\n我就有保留嘅<br />\n<br />\n原因係：<br />\n勇武係有效阻嚇對家用暴力<br />\n但對於宜家對家破窗效應嘅速度比我地變勇武快<br />\n好多手足都係無殘暴對待別人嘅心<br />\n同埋狗同愛字頭嘅人渣合作無間<br />\n正面勇武係唔著數<br />\n要勇就要暗地裡 打遊擊 佢地完場先黎逐個反擊<br />\n<br />\n講返正題先 今次唔係想講勇武策略<br />\n<br />\n大型和理非行動宜家戰爭狀態效果其實都好大<br />\n係connect到全世界<br />\n<br />\n一般人已經對連儂牆有麻木感，我覺得都要keep嘅，但效果上大家都知已經細左好多<br />\n908美領遊行果張大卷連儂牆<br />\n講真真係好細<br />\n同埋整大型野應該要遠距離都睇到內容<br />\n唔係就效果就大打折扣<br />\n<br />\n我同fd有個提議<br />\n以915和理非活動做例子<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一人一張A3顏色紙</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">寫上我地嘅口號</span></span><br />\n將遊行隊伍變成超大型流動連儂牆<br />\n我相信個視覺效果上會再次震撼全球<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地要keep住個運動嘅溫度</span></span><br />\n就要keep住創造更多世界第一次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cYYGBb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcYYGBb6.jpg&h=dec46b07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以手足們<br />\n一方面要提升勇武心要有戰鬥意識<br />\n另一方面要創造多啲唔同有話題嘅和理非行動<br />\n<br />\n雙管齊下先有機會抗衡到咁強嘅對手<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n天佑吾城"},{"pid":"e817057677fc6812ed5eb463b0a52517ef3c815a","tid":1568724,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5449141698aa64b841936c70e9803911ff72233","tid":1568724,"uid":201816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:10:49.000Z","msg":"915 915 915<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好唔記得915啊<br />\n大家快D幫手推上熱門啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568633\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568633</a>"},{"pid":"bc5d4475a8fe7d7bea12b6e533c9ab97e744bb61","tid":1568724,"uid":297981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:13:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1bcb301724890ae8420a521a73169461577acd","tid":1568724,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e680cfcecd42afa44d2c03aae760a5b14f2edb73","tid":1568724,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:16:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"163e9dece149c7c3825454b635d53cda1c3bacff","tid":1568724,"uid":101963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:16:46.000Z","msg":"對付藍絲應該借力打力，順水推舟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568616\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568616</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"418321970057a2a06e1ff095abb296ff89e77953","tid":1568724,"uid":238808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"915 915<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6be24ead4aee7636c3cad3fc2cf58ace27b6549","tid":1568724,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"聽日算好天 G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667cb7359c9b528b3989a1011355e072c188dc6e","tid":1568724,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit